 />\n其實返工點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一返到去會覺得好撚辛苦"},{"pid":"e6ea12b3f5417bfdd473de6f1321b2e961fba844","tid":129503,"uid":65751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"5.5hr啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到公司全靠一杯咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7bdcc1f7ce6a102218c7a51bbcc42ae16eda40","tid":129503,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常兩點幾訓，7點起身<br />\n<br />\n星期六，日就4，5點先訓，12點幾起身</blockquote><br />\n其實返工點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一返到去會覺得好撚辛苦</blockquote><br />\n慣左掛<br />\n<br />\n我返工車程個幾鐘都會訓一陣既<br />\n<br />\n返到公司就沖杯茶飲下提一提神<br />\n<br />\n咁就踩足一日<br />\n<br />\n我都想早訓，但唔知點解磨下磨下就兩點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b5eefd10ead0ec56113f012eaf50cc7a98266","tid":129503,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常兩點幾訓，7點起身<br />\n<br />\n星期六，日就4，5點先訓，12點幾起身</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4b72eef0c63af959a319afb84d94ca0bc5e4ce","tid":129503,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"點可以日日訓三四個鐘仲可以生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}